                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-67-off368 t17970712-67-cd369"></join>, a gold chain necklace, value 1l. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17970712-67-victim718" type="victimName">
                        John Benjamin 
                        Cole
                     <interp inst="t17970712-67-victim718" type="surname" value="Cole"></interp>
